# IOUSBInterfaceAssociationDescriptor

## Declaration

```swift
struct IOUSBInterfaceAssociationDescriptor {
   UInt8 bLength;
   UInt8 bDescriptorType;
   UInt8 bFirstInterface;
   UInt8 bInterfaceCount;
   UInt8 bFunctionClass;
   UInt8 bFunctionSubClass;
   UInt8 bFunctionProtocol;
   UInt8 iFunction;
};
```

## Overview

USB Inerface Association Descriptor. ECN to the USB 2.0 Spec. See the USB Specification at [link-1670329].

## Related Documentation

- **IOUSBInterfaceAssociationDescriptor**: The descriptor that associates multiple interfaces to the same function.
